headline: Should you buy Netflix stock? Wolfe Research, WarrenAI weigh in
summary: Investing.com -- Netflix Inc (NASDAQ:NFLX) shares have surged 65% over the past 12 months, outperforming the Nasdaq Composite, yet analysts remain split on whether this rally has room left to run. Wolfe Research is firmly in the bullish camp, citing durable growth, a premium content strategy, and a valuation premium justified by strong earnings momentum.
